item.description:
An Estafette extension is in essence just a containerized application. What's special is that it uses custom properties injected as environment variables to parameterize it's behaviour.
In the example below all non-reserved properties are automatically turned into a environment variable prefixed with ESTAFETTE_EXTENSION_.
bake: image: extensions/docker:dev action: build repositories: - estafette In this example the action property is set as ESTAFETTE_EXTENSION_ACTION on the stage container; the repositories property is set as ESTAFETTE_EXTENSION_REPOSITORIES and it's array items are joined into comma-separated value;
